long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ЁЯУг  Overview:
This extension has been developed to enable the retrieval of email addresses from PDF documents. It offers the capability to extract emails from chosen pages or from all pages within a PDF file. During extraction, it captures information such as the email address and the corresponding page number.

ЁЯЪА  Main Features:
тЬЕ  Extraction of email addresses and page numbers is supported.
тЬЕ  Option to select specific pages for extraction.
тЬЕ  Functionality to export extraction Emails to CSV or XLSX formats.

Is It Free?
тЬФя╕П Absolutely! The basic functions are completely free to use, with the possibility to upgrade for additional features.

ЁЯФТ  Privacy and Security:
Protecting your privacy is paramount to us. All extracted data are processed locally and will never be transmitted to our servers. We do not store your data.
